extend layout

block content
  h1 Members Area
  p Welcome to the members area
  p
    | Vivamus hendrerit arcu sed erat molestie
    | vehicula. Sed auctor neque eu tellus
    | rhoncus ut eleifend nibh porttitor. Ut in.
  p
    | Donec congue lacinia dui, a porttitor
    | lectus condimentum laoreet. Nunc eu
    | ullamcorper orci. Quisque eget odio ac
    | lectus vestibulum faucibus eget in metus.
    | In pellentesque faucibus vestibulum. Nulla
    | at nulla justo, eget luctus tortor.

    if users
      p
        strong Name : 
        | #{users.name}
      p
        strong Email : 
        | #{users.email}
      p
        strong Username : 
        | #{users.username}
      table(style={'width':'fit-content','padding':'0px'}) 
        tr
          th(style={'text-align':'left','padding':'0px','width':'auto'}) Select Session No. to view session details : 
          td
            select.form-control(id='session_no' name="session_no")
              option(hidden) Select Session No.
                if sessions 
                  each session,i in sessions
                    option(value='#{i+1}') #{i+1}
      if sessions
        each session, i in sessions
          div(id='session_id_#{i+1}',style='display:none',class='session_details')
            strong Session No. #{i+1} 
            li
              strong vehicle_id : 
              |  #{session.vehicle_id}
            li
              strong session_start : 
              |  #{new Date(session.session_start + new Date().getTimezoneOffset()*60000)}
            li
              strong session_end : 
              |  #{new Date(session.session_end + new Date().getTimezoneOffset()*60000)}

